items.title: More than 50 people injured in mosque blast at Jakarta high school
items.description: Authorities say a 17-year-old suspected of causing the explosion during Friday prayers is in surgery.

items.title: Kenya demands safety for its citizens after Tanzania's post-poll crackdown
items.description: Some Kenyans have reportedly been killed, injured and others detained by Tanzanian security officers.

items.title: Elon Musk's $1tn pay deal approved by Tesla shareholders
items.description: The richest man in the world will get hundreds of millions of new shares if he hits his targets.

items.title: China launches new aircraft carrier in naval race with the US
items.description: The Fujian uses electromagnetic catapults that allow planes to strike from a greater distance.

items.title: Multiple people fall ill after package delivered to Air Force One base
items.description: The building the package was opened in was evacuated and those taken ill were found to be stable.
